            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Albi Vitalionis che<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>lidon</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>opobalsam</abbr><ex>atum</ex></expan> ad calig<supplied reason="lost">inem</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Albi Vitalionis mixtum ad <lb n="2"/>omnia praeter <expan><abbr>lippitudin</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Albi Vitalionis melinum <lb n="2"/>acre ad <expan><abbr>pulver</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>caligine</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Albi Vi</supplied>talionis isochrysum <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ad in</supplied>cipientes <expan><abbr>suffus</abbr><ex>iones</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>clar</abbr><ex>itatem</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> SAT<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>s
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Augenarztstempel. Z. 9 befindet sich auf der Oberseite; dort Buchstabe A mit spitz nach unten zeigender Querhaste. Z. 9: Schreibtechnik: eingeritzt. (B): Provost, in: Provost u. a., La Côte d&amp;apos;Or: Z. 3/4: Zeilenfall fehlt; Z. 6 (Ende): caligin(em) t(ollendas); CIL 13, 10021, 44; ILS: Z. 6 (Ende): caligine(m); Provost, in: Provost u. a., La Côte d&amp;apos;Or: Z. 7: Vit]alionis; ILS; Provost, in: Provost u. a., La Côte d&amp;apos;Or: Z. 9 nicht wiedergegeben.</p>
            </div>
